T1  - International capital mobility, the factor content of trade and Leontief paradoxes
AU  - Gaisford, James D.
JO  - Journal of International Economics
VL  - 39
IS  - 1
SP  - 175
EP  - 183
PY  - 1995
DA  - 1995/08/01/
SN  - 0022-1996
